146
00:10:06,569 --> 00:10:07,569
Should she?

147
00:10:07,569 --> 00:10:11,569
What do you mean, can it be that you just said, should she?

148
00:10:11,569 --> 00:10:14,569
I'll eat again when you write the letter.

149
00:10:14,569 --> 00:10:16,569
So no, that's not to be understood.

150
00:10:16,569 --> 00:10:21,569
You are unwise, Miss Clara, and I have to say it, also undressed.

151
00:10:21,569 --> 00:10:25,569
But you are intelligent enough to know what to do with it.

152
00:10:25,791 --> 00:10:28,591
I know that very well, but I don't care.

153
00:10:28,591 --> 00:10:32,291
I'm shocked. Shocked and very disappointed.

154
00:10:32,291 --> 00:10:34,291
I didn't expect that from you.

155
00:10:34,291 --> 00:10:35,791
I don't care.

156
00:10:35,791 --> 00:10:36,791
What do you mean?

157
00:10:36,791 --> 00:10:39,291
Don't act as if you didn't understand.

158
00:10:39,291 --> 00:10:41,291
I want you to write the letter.

159
00:10:41,291 --> 00:10:44,291
Be reasonable. That's not possible.

160
00:10:44,291 --> 00:10:45,291
Why?

161
00:10:45,791 --> 00:10:47,791
It's possible.

162
00:10:51,291 --> 00:10:54,791
I won't eat anything until you write to my father.

163
00:10:54,911 --> 00:10:55,911
But...

164
00:11:05,849 --> 00:11:10,849
Well, fine. I'll ask your father to come home. He'll decide for himself.

165
00:11:10,849 --> 00:11:12,849
Unfortunately, I can't bear that responsibility.

166
00:11:12,849 --> 00:11:14,849
Good. Write it down for sure, okay?

167
00:11:14,849 --> 00:11:16,849
Don't change your mind anymore?

168
00:11:16,849 --> 00:11:18,849
Yes, I'll write it down. You've won.

169
00:11:18,849 --> 00:11:20,849
But I'll also write that I'm against it.

170
00:11:20,849 --> 00:11:24,849
Write the letter down for tonight. Then we can send it to you tomorrow.

171
00:11:24,849 --> 00:11:25,849
Thank you.

172
00:11:25,849 --> 00:11:27,849
Yes, please.

173
00:11:27,849 --> 00:11:31,849
Sebastian! Sebastian, I'm hungry!

174
00:11:35,849 --> 00:11:37,849
Come on!

175
00:11:45,849 --> 00:11:47,849
Heidi!

176
00:11:47,849 --> 00:11:52,849
Good morning! Did the postman give you a letter for me today, Peter?

177
00:11:52,849 --> 00:11:55,849
No, why should he?

178
00:11:55,929 --> 00:11:58,929
Then Clara can't read my handwriting after all.

179
00:11:58,929 --> 00:12:00,929
Of course, Clara.

180
00:12:00,929 --> 00:12:02,929
You can't write to me, can you?

181
00:12:02,929 --> 00:12:04,929
You don't believe how happy you can be.

182
00:12:04,929 --> 00:12:07,929
You couldn't read my handwriting after all.

183
