Tell me, what's wrong with you?

185
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:23,510
You're slowly getting on my nerves.

186
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:26,510
I can't change that either.

187
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:28,510
What is it now? Are you coming?

188
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:32,510
No, I'm not going with you anymore. I'm going home. I have to write a letter.

189
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:33,510
You're crazy.

190
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:35,510
Fine, then I'm crazy.

191
00:12:36,510 --> 00:12:38,510
