192
00:12:42,926 --> 00:12:45,926
What do you want here?

193
00:12:45,926 --> 00:12:48,926
No, little ghost, you belong to your herd.

194
00:12:48,926 --> 00:12:51,926
Now eat well so you can grow, okay?

195
00:12:51,926 --> 00:12:52,926
Go on!

196
00:12:52,926 --> 00:12:55,926
No, no, no, I don't have time to play with you today.

197
00:12:55,926 --> 00:12:59,926
Run to the other little ghosts, and fast!

198
00:13:01,926 --> 00:13:03,926
I said fast!

199
00:13:10,766 --> 00:13:13,766
For Clara, she throws us away like an old roller.

200
00:13:13,766 --> 00:13:40,766
Love...

201
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:44,910
Finally you're fine. I'm fine too.

202
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:50,910
This time you can read my handwriting for sure.

203
00:14:04,686 --> 00:14:06,686
I'm home again, Clara!

204
00:14:06,686 --> 00:14:08,686
Papa, finally, papa!

205
00:14:10,686 --> 00:14:12,686
Nice, you look very good, my child.

206
00:14:12,686 --> 00:14:14,686
I thought you were very pale.

207
00:14:14,686 --> 00:14:16,686
Mrs. Rottenmeier wrote you were on a hunger strike.

208
00:14:16,686 --> 00:14:17,686
What's going on?

209
00:14:17,686 --> 00:14:20,686
I wanted to, too. I was afraid you'd forget the promise you gave me.

210
00:14:20,686 --> 00:14:23,686
And you almost did, didn't you?

211
00:14:23,686 --> 00:14:25,686
How did you know?

212
00:14:25,686 --> 00:14:28,686
Clara, I just wanted to talk to you.

213
00:14:28,686 --> 00:14:31,686
You don't need to. I want to visit Heidi.

214
00:14:32,916 --> 00:14:35,216
Who says you're not supposed to do that, child?

215
00:14:35,216 --> 00:14:38,416
Yes, but why do we have to talk then?

216
00:14:38,416 --> 00:14:42,616
Because I want you to realize that I have to talk to the doctor first.

217
00:14:42,616 --> 00:14:45,016
I want to leave the decision to him.

218
00:14:45,016 --> 00:14:49,616
He knows best what is wrong for you and what is right for you.

219
00:14:49,616 --> 00:14:53,516
And I stupid man thought you kept your promise.

220
00:14:53,516 --> 00:14:57,016
But Clara, what am I supposed to do?

221
00:14:57,016 --> 00:15:00,016
Just keep your promise. I don't want any more.

222
00:15:00,222 --> 00:15:03,822
You are very strict and very unfair to me, Clara, do you know that?

223
00:15:04,022 --> 00:15:06,622
I know my promise and I want to keep it.

224
00:15:07,622 --> 00:15:10,022
I want to see Heidi, Dad, please.

225
00:15:13,222 --> 00:15:14,022
What is it?

226
00:15:14,222 --> 00:15:16,222
The Herr Geheimrat wants to speak to you.

227
00:15:16,422 --> 00:15:18,422
Don't worry, child, I'll be done with him.

228
