Maybe to the North Sea or the Baltic Sea.

234
00:15:44,099 --> 00:15:48,099
I am undecided if I only knew how the weather will be.

235
00:15:48,099 --> 00:15:53,099
Well, I heard up there on the coast there should be a number of very nice
islands.

236
00:15:53,099 --> 00:15:56,099
Yes, that's why I thought about it.

237
00:15:56,553 --> 00:15:59,553
But you're right, it can be very rough up there.

238
00:15:59,553 --> 00:16:02,553
What do you think of Baden-Baden? My mother was there last year.

239
00:16:02,553 --> 00:16:04,553
She says it would be very pleasant.

240
00:16:04,553 --> 00:16:08,553
Yes, in a healing town, to Wiesbaden, for example, that's an idea.

241
00:16:08,553 --> 00:16:11,553
Peace, peace, hot springs.

242
00:16:11,553 --> 00:16:14,553
I think I have reason to thank you, Mr. Sesemann.

243
00:16:14,553 --> 00:16:17,553
Wiesbaden is a pretty town and I don't have to drive far yet.

244
00:16:17,553 --> 00:16:19,553
I knew something else for you.

245
00:16:19,553 --> 00:16:21,553
Yes, you make me curious.

246
00:16:21,553 --> 00:16:22,553
Where are you sending me?

247
00:16:22,553 --> 00:16:23,553
To the Alps.

248
00:16:23,881 --> 00:16:27,681
What? I've been to the Alps every summer for ten years.

249
00:16:27,681 --> 00:16:29,281
It's beautiful there.

250
00:16:29,281 --> 00:16:35,081
Splendid clear air, flowers, cows, goats, but I actually wanted to see something
different.

251
00:16:35,081 --> 00:16:40,481
Hm, if it's so beautiful in the mountains, wouldn't that be something for our
Clara?

252
00:16:40,481 --> 00:16:41,681
For your daughter?

253
00:16:41,681 --> 00:16:46,681
Well, air change wouldn't be bad for her, but whether that's the right thing to
do...

254
00:16:47,129 --> 00:16:52,129
I'm convinced that the fresh air, the peace, the peace, the good milk would be
good for her.

255
00:16:52,129 --> 00:16:54,129
But she can't use her wheelchair.

256
